    "en": {
      "title": "40,000 metric tons of diesel will reach Colombo tonight",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ministry of Energy said this afternoon (15) that a ship carrying 40,000 metric tons of diesel is scheduled to arrive in Colombo tonight (15) and the diesel stock will start unloading tomorrow morning.",
        "The officer further mentioned that as soon as the vehicles have finished unloading, they will distribute the diesel to the filling stations and hope to provide more quantity to the filling stations."
      ],
